<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B5106046"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
When piston stroke is out of specification, select reverse clutch retaining plate with suitable thickness from among the following table and replace it.
</ptxt>
